Jehovah skillfully used his dynamic energy

00:08:24.339 --> 00:08:27.339
to make all the matter of the universe.

00:08:27.339 --> 00:08:33.169
The heavens are declaring the glory of God

00:08:33.169 --> 00:08:36.169
and up the work of his hands,

00:08:36.169 --> 00:08:40.919
the expanse is telling.

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:42.919
In modern times,

00:08:42.919 --> 00:08:49.480
we have peered into the far reaches of space

00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:53.480
and seen creation at an awe-inspiring scale.

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:59.100
Yours, O Jehovah,

00:08:59.100 --> 00:09:03.100
are the greatness and the excellency.

00:09:03.100 --> 00:09:07.100
Everything in the heavens is yours.

00:09:07.100 --> 00:09:09.100
In your hand,

00:09:09.100 --> 00:09:15.980
there are power and mightiness.

00:09:15.980 --> 00:09:19.980
When we raise our eyes to the heavens,

00:09:19.980 --> 00:09:24.980
we are seeing evidence of Jehovah's unparalleled power.

00:09:24.980 --> 00:09:38.320
Jehovah is powerful,

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:41.320
but do you really think he cares about each of us here?

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:43.320
He shows that he cares

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:45.320
and how he designed a comfortable home

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:47.320
made just right for us.

